sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>AlertListPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AlertListView
    participant SER as AlertListSerializer
    participant MW as TierDatabaseMiddleware
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Alerts page
    FE->>API: GET /api/alerts/
    API->>MW: __call__(request)
    MW->>MW: set_db_for_role(user.role)
    MW-->>API: DB routed to free_db
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.all().order_by("-timestamp")
    DB-->>API: QuerySet[Alert]
    API->>SER: AlertListSerializer(alerts, many=True)
    SER-->>API: Serialized alert list
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {results: [...], count}
    FE-->>U: Render alert table with severity badges
